| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0033 — Mass File Rename (netwalker)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 232c57a6-e134-5a8c-9d64-0df5d826902b"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
